  "detailed_description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/6695e41b09044e6454e9f2eb198d271f.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/6695e41b09044e6454e9f2eb198d271f.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/6695e41b09044e6454e9f2eb198d271f.mp4?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/2e2f10195c8caca10c31b235641a22a6.webp?t=1717088931\" width=369 height=58 /></span><br>The capital calls for aid, and the people of Konvila will not stand alone. But after witnessing the horrifying scene of the commander's death, your army was routed. As the highest-ranking officer to survive, the responsibility falls to you, captain, to lead your people and reform the line.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/dbd9a8d29568182a486d88f33c8719e2.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/dbd9a8d29568182a486d88f33c8719e2.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/dbd9a8d29568182a486d88f33c8719e2.mp4?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/3558266f6cc8bb50211700905ed5a538.webp?t=1717088931\" width=251 height=58 /></span><br>The Banner of Blood is a medieval fantasy game infused with action and rogue-like elements. Players will find themselves up against the ever-growing forces of evil, relying on their courage and powerful relics to fend off formidable armies of foes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make your way through the vast orc-infested weald to reach the kingdom's heartland. Every journey will be unique and filled with challenges.</li><li>Regroup your scattered troops and recruit volunteers. You'll need anyone who can wield a weapon in the battles ahead.</li><li>Reclaim the relics lost in the chaos of war, as they hold the keys to victory.</li><li>Battle dreadful monsters that have joined forces with bloodlust-driven orcs.</li><li>Permadeath - You are strong, but not invincible. Even if you fall, your courage will pave the path for the next brave soul to take up the mantle.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.mp4?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/d2ef6ba7e3290fafbd26af7a4c19513b.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/d2ef6ba7e3290fafbd26af7a4c19513b.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/d2ef6ba7e3290fafbd26af7a4c19513b.mp4?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
