ht=58 /></span><br>The Banner of Blood is a medieval fantasy game infused with action and rogue-like elements. Players will find themselves up against the ever-growing forces of evil, relying on their courage and powerful relics to fend off formidable armies of foes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make your way through the vast orc-infested weald to reach the kingdom's heartland. Every journey will be unique and filled with challenges.</li><li>Regroup your scattered troops and recruit volunteers. You'll need anyone who can wield a weapon in the battles ahead.</li><li>Reclaim the relics lost in the chaos of war, as they hold the keys to victory.</li><li>Battle dreadful monsters that have joined forces with bloodlust-driven orcs.</li><li>Permadeath - You are strong, but not invincible. Even if you fall, your courage will pave the path for the next brave soul to take up the mantle.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/fad120a268fb675dcc9c9cb48b0f0d9e.mp4?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/d2ef6ba7e3290fafbd26af7a4c19513b.poster.avif?t=1717088931\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922670/extras/d2ef6ba7e3290fafbd26af7a4c19513b.webm?t=1717088931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.ak